requested, your power,

00:14:59.041 --> 00:15:02.163
your strength and fortification on behalf

00:15:02.243 --> 00:15:04.085
of your EBED coworker.

00:15:05.365 --> 00:15:08.008
You and I want to liberate the sun

00:15:10.227 --> 00:15:13.808
Saving through the Son by delivering your

00:15:14.109 --> 00:15:14.269
Amah.

00:15:14.288 --> 00:15:19.390
Yahowah's Amah, motherly coworker.

00:15:20.551 --> 00:15:22.371
That is how the Son who saved us

00:15:23.731 --> 00:15:24.231
was saved.

00:15:25.753 --> 00:15:26.913
We have God's word on it.

00:15:28.192 --> 00:15:30.594
You have decided to act engaging with me

00:15:30.673 --> 00:15:34.335
such that you working with me serves to

00:15:34.475 --> 00:15:36.916
provide for me a genuinely good life.

00:15:37.909 --> 00:15:39.610
resolutely moral,

00:15:40.331 --> 00:15:42.131
an overtly positive sign,

00:15:42.211 --> 00:15:45.332
a miraculous symbol of femininity whose

00:15:45.452 --> 00:15:48.053
attitude and aptitude are especially

00:15:48.094 --> 00:15:49.355
productive and beneficial.

00:15:51.216 --> 00:15:54.277
Then those who have shunned and abhorred

00:15:54.317 --> 00:15:56.758
me, those who dislike and slight me,

00:15:57.278 --> 00:15:59.918
may choose to see and understand and be

00:15:59.979 --> 00:16:02.440
ashamed and even humiliated for that

00:16:02.500 --> 00:16:04.961
decision because you, Yahowah,

00:16:05.942 --> 00:16:06.562
supported me.

00:16:07.457 --> 00:16:09.359
helping and assisting me.

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.620
And you consoled me,

00:16:12.321 --> 00:16:13.841
relenting regarding me,

00:16:14.942 --> 00:16:20.446
reconsidering your disposition toward me.

00:16:20.466 --> 00:16:22.287
These last two statements were from the

00:16:22.346 --> 00:16:23.567
Eighty-Sixth Mizmowr,

00:16:24.148 --> 00:16:26.269
the Sixteenth and Seventeenth Statements.

00:16:27.070 --> 00:16:28.811
Moving now to the Hundred and Sixteenth.

00:16:29.796 --> 00:16:31.197
Oh, yeah, indeed, it's true.

00:16:31.897 --> 00:16:33.217
I am your coworker.

00:16:33.937 --> 00:16:34.899
I am your servant,

00:16:35.558 --> 00:16:38.260
the son of your Amah,

00:16:38.740 --> 00:16:41.863
productive mother and coworker.

00:16:42.163 --> 00:16:45.304
You have responded to open and release

00:16:45.345 --> 00:16:47.206
that which pertains to my bonds,

00:16:47.927 --> 00:16:50.687
freeing me from my punishment through

00:16:50.748 --> 00:16:55.750
disciplined instruction.

00:16:55.770 --> 00:16:58.432
Pretty amazing how explicit God is

00:16:59.337 --> 00:17:01.899
and revealing what the world has missed

00:17:02.421 --> 00:17:03.020
heretofore.

00:17:05.182 --> 00:17:05.363
Now,

00:17:05.522 --> 00:17:10.847
just affirming something that I had long

00:17:13.529 --> 00:17:14.691
perceived as true.

00:17:16.553 --> 00:17:20.195
The Choter that Dowd introduces in the

00:17:20.476 --> 00:17:25.259
fourteenth Mashal isn't actually coming

00:17:25.319 --> 00:17:27.142
from the stem of

00:17:28.314 --> 00:17:28.794
Yshay.

00:17:29.654 --> 00:17:32.778
He's here to replace Yshay.

00:17:34.638 --> 00:17:37.461
A choter stem will be extended out of

00:17:37.500 --> 00:17:38.001
the stump,

00:17:38.021 --> 00:17:41.044
which has been cut down so that it

00:17:41.084 --> 00:17:42.986
is capable of supporting new growth.

00:17:44.258 --> 00:17:46.838
Of Yshay, to stand out and be noticed,

00:17:47.259 --> 00:17:49.319
drawing attention to the substance of

00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:51.740
existence as a Netser,

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:53.642
an observant branch,

00:17:54.182 --> 00:17:56.323
by means of its roots and that which

00:17:56.363 --> 00:17:57.423
keeps it anchored,

00:17:57.563 --> 00:17:58.763
steadfast and nourished,

00:17:59.483 --> 00:18:01.345
such that he will continually bear an

00:18:01.384 --> 00:18:02.384
abundance of fruit,

00:18:03.204 --> 00:18:05.385
being productive as a bull while

00:18:05.405 --> 00:18:07.707
encouraging productivity in others.

00:18:10.673 --> 00:18:12.015
So with these insights,

00:18:12.035 --> 00:18:13.954
that was Isaiah eleven one,

00:18:14.655 --> 00:18:19.897
we're going to go through this recap of

00:18:19.938 --> 00:18:20.998
the final word picture.

00:18:22.578 --> 00:18:24.099
It reads the Dabarym,

00:18:24.720 --> 00:18:29.061
the words of Lamow 'El Melek,

00:18:30.221 --> 00:18:31.883
the sovereign counselor and king,

00:18:32.962 --> 00:18:34.564
inseparable from God.

00:18:37.554 --> 00:18:40.476
This is a profoundly poignant prophetic

00:18:40.517 --> 00:18:43.439
pronouncement, a heavy burden to be borne,

00:18:44.680 --> 00:18:46.902
while paying tribute to someone

00:18:47.663 --> 00:18:50.785
tremendously uplifting with strong,

00:18:51.705 --> 00:18:52.826
heartfelt yearnings,

00:18:53.708 --> 00:18:57.029
revealed in a prophecy pertaining to the

00:18:57.069 --> 00:18:59.031
past as well as to the future.

00:19:00.653 --> 00:19:04.056
That is a benefit of the relationship and

00:19:04.195 --> 00:19:05.096
to reveal the way.

00:19:05.637 --> 00:19:05.857
Asher.

00:19:07.603 --> 00:19:13.064
This Em, his mother,

00:19:13.084 --> 00:19:16.904
taught this to him for the express purpose

00:19:17.684 --> 00:19:18.505
of correcting him.

00:19:21.965 --> 00:19:27.727
Mashal Proverbs, thirty-one-one.

00:19:27.787 --> 00:19:30.487
Who and when is the question?

00:19:32.048 --> 00:19:34.268
My radiant and bright chosen son,

00:19:36.479 --> 00:19:39.320
Ponder how and why my favorite child and

00:19:39.361 --> 00:19:42.923
thoughtful boy conceived within my place

00:19:42.962 --> 00:19:43.462
of origin.

00:19:44.462 --> 00:19:47.545
Consider what and where my chosen son

00:19:47.605 --> 00:19:50.446
whose brilliance is reflected in the

00:19:50.487 --> 00:19:54.368
moonlight and for whom I selected for this

00:19:54.429 --> 00:19:59.791
relationship via my vow and binding

00:19:59.852 --> 00:20:00.251
promise.

00:20:05.009 --> 00:20:08.290
Do not ever offer or give your

00:20:08.391 --> 00:20:10.593
authorization, your qualifications,

00:20:10.613 --> 00:20:16.136
your competency to women or your journey

00:20:16.156 --> 00:20:19.239
through life to someone who conceals the

00:20:19.259 --> 00:20:22.020
truth and destroys those with the

00:20:22.141 --> 00:20:23.902
authorization to lead.

00:20:25.363 --> 00:20:28.924
It is not for those authorized to govern,

00:20:29.586 --> 00:20:32.887
Lamuw'el, one inseparable from God.

00:20:33.654 --> 00:20:35.756
No, it's not for kings,

00:20:35.856 --> 00:20:38.557
for counselors and leaders to be drunk

00:20:40.420 --> 00:20:42.941
with wine or for those who govern in

00:20:43.020 --> 00:20:46.943
a significant or judicious capacity to

00:20:47.044 --> 00:20:49.665
crave intoxicating libations.

00:20:53.067 --> 00:20:53.548
Otherwise,

00:20:53.587 --> 00:20:56.851
perhaps he would continually get drunk and

00:20:56.990 --> 00:20:57.371
forget,

00:20:57.431 --> 00:21:00.452
even overlook and ignore that which has

00:21:00.492 --> 00:21:03.335
been written as inscribed prescriptions.

00:21:04.897 --> 00:21:05.478
and change,

00:21:06.137 --> 00:21:09.118
creating a different variation each year

00:21:09.338 --> 00:21:12.578
of the means to determine and distinguish

00:21:12.618 --> 00:21:13.920
between right and wrong,

00:21:14.819 --> 00:21:19.060
exercising good judgment regarding all of

00:21:19.121 --> 00:21:21.540
the children of the afflicted and

00:21:21.621 --> 00:21:22.121
suffering,

00:21:22.141 --> 00:21:27.162
the harassed and even the persecuted.

00:21:27.221 --> 00:21:32.262
So you can offer, should you want,

00:21:33.277 --> 00:21:35.378
Intoxicating beverages to the one who is

00:21:35.459 --> 00:21:36.720
already lost and dying,

00:21:37.560 --> 00:21:39.242
having squandered their life away.

00:21:40.544 --> 00:21:42.425
And wine to the embittered and

00:21:42.486 --> 00:21:43.747
disagreeable soul.

00:21:45.607 --> 00:21:47.810
He can habitually drink to the point of

00:21:47.891 --> 00:21:50.573
constant intoxication and forget his

00:21:50.633 --> 00:21:53.095
impoverished state of incapacitation as a

00:21:53.134 --> 00:21:56.538
result of his meekness and ignorance.

00:21:58.099 --> 00:21:58.380
And then...

00:21:59.332 --> 00:22:01.953
His unpleasant and distressful situation

00:22:01.993 --> 00:22:05.236
and resulting misadventures will no longer

00:22:05.256 --> 00:22:09.259
be known or remembered.

00:22:09.940 --> 00:22:10.819
Open your mouth,

00:22:11.760 --> 00:22:15.063
speak boldly for those without a voice

00:22:16.163 --> 00:22:18.144
concerning the defense and the cause of

00:22:18.326 --> 00:22:21.127
every child who was destitute and

00:22:21.147 --> 00:22:22.127
abandoned.

00:22:23.148 --> 00:22:27.172
Open your mouth, communicating profusely,

00:22:28.167 --> 00:22:30.689
when choosing to lead and litigate,

00:22:31.470 --> 00:22:34.230
making sound decisions correctly,

00:22:35.172 --> 00:22:36.452
honestly and justly,

00:22:37.053 --> 00:22:39.855
thereby electing to exercise good

00:22:39.894 --> 00:22:40.335
judgment,

00:22:41.516 --> 00:22:45.077
governing and defending the responsive as

00:22:45.137 --> 00:22:45.897
well as the willing.

00:22:49.099 --> 00:22:51.280
How is he to find,

00:22:52.402 --> 00:22:54.143
to obtain and experience

00:22:55.663 --> 00:22:58.865
a strong and capable woman of noble

00:22:58.904 --> 00:23:02.968
character who is as enriching as she is

00:23:03.167 --> 00:23:06.849
virtuous, far more valuable than rubies,

00:23:07.089 --> 00:23:09.771
corals, or even jewels.

00:23:12.334 --> 00:23:15.115
Can he confide in her?

00:23:16.115 --> 00:23:18.837
Will he confidently trust her,

00:23:18.897 --> 00:23:22.099
relying on her during missteps and still

00:23:22.140 --> 00:23:22.799
feel safe?

00:23:22.900 --> 00:23:23.941
Whoa, what a...

00:23:25.825 --> 00:23:27.046
an insightful statement.

00:23:28.326 --> 00:23:31.307
Dowd had chosen women because they were

00:23:31.387 --> 00:23:35.490
either politically positioned to enhance

00:23:35.569 --> 00:23:40.373
his status or they were pretty pretty.

00:23:41.673 --> 00:23:43.453
And he simply coveted them for the way

00:23:43.473 --> 00:23:43.913
they looked.

00:23:45.414 --> 00:23:47.615
And here, this adoptive mother,

00:23:48.576 --> 00:23:50.877
the one who would save him from himself,

00:23:52.280 --> 00:23:53.001
I said, you know,

00:23:53.021 --> 00:23:55.644
there's something vastly more valuable

00:23:55.684 --> 00:23:58.288
than that, son.

00:23:58.327 --> 00:24:00.049
Finding a woman that you can confide in.

00:24:02.012 --> 00:24:03.914
Someone you can genuinely trust.

00:24:05.237 --> 00:24:06.617
Someone you can rely upon,

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:10.482
even during missteps and still feel safe.

00:24:13.483 --> 00:24:16.365
One of the beautiful insights here is not

00:24:16.566 --> 00:24:18.207
only the depth of character that would

00:24:18.247 --> 00:24:21.710
allow that and the budding of trust that

00:24:21.750 --> 00:24:25.913
causes this to happen and the great joy

00:24:25.952 --> 00:24:28.494
of being able to rely on someone in

00:24:28.535 --> 00:24:31.356
this regard is that Yahowah,

00:24:32.738 --> 00:24:36.160
rather than trying to avoid us having a

00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:39.242
misstep, wants us to stumble and fall.

00:24:40.763 --> 00:24:42.525
He doesn't want us to be perfect.

00:24:43.410 --> 00:24:45.172
He wants us to make mistakes.

00:24:46.292 --> 00:24:49.255
He wants us to fail.

00:24:49.756 --> 00:24:50.096
Why?

00:24:50.616 --> 00:24:52.678
Because it is only through failure that we

00:24:52.718 --> 00:24:55.701
can demonstrate that we have what's in,

00:24:56.721 --> 00:24:59.644
that which needs to be in us to

00:24:59.664 --> 00:25:01.705
have the character to succeed,

00:25:02.988 --> 00:25:04.828
to show that we can succeed.

00:25:05.750 --> 00:25:07.632
It is only through obstacles that we can

00:25:07.672 --> 00:25:09.634
show that we know how to overcome them.

00:25:10.685 --> 00:25:12.567
It is by falling that we prove that

00:25:12.606 --> 00:25:13.788
we can get back up.

00:25:14.567 --> 00:25:16.429
It is by making a mistake that we

00:25:16.489 --> 00:25:22.392
show we're capable of learning.

00:25:22.412 --> 00:25:23.951
So this is really quite brilliant.

00:25:24.011 --> 00:25:27.993
It's one of the more recent deductions we

00:25:28.034 --> 00:25:30.515
have made in restudying the events of the

00:25:30.535 --> 00:25:30.976
garden.

00:25:32.296 --> 00:25:34.057
That there wasn't an initial sin.

00:25:34.777 --> 00:25:37.798
That Eve, who was actually Chawah,

00:25:37.979 --> 00:25:39.940
didn't cause the problem.

00:25:41.325 --> 00:25:43.006
that Yahowah foreclosed on the garden

00:25:43.046 --> 00:25:46.307
experience because he wanted man to fall

00:25:47.449 --> 00:25:49.309
so that we could demonstrate the capacity

00:25:49.329 --> 00:25:50.049
to get back up,

00:25:50.711 --> 00:25:52.172
so that we can prove that we could

00:25:52.192 --> 00:25:55.993
be trusted.

00:25:56.034 --> 00:25:57.535
That's the point she's making here,

00:25:57.714 --> 00:25:58.855
but she's also saying,

00:25:59.215 --> 00:26:01.557
wouldn't it be great if when you stumble

00:26:01.656 --> 00:26:03.298
and fall, when you make a mistake,

00:26:04.138 --> 00:26:06.240
that you could have a strong woman there

00:26:06.279 --> 00:26:07.361
that you could confide in,

00:26:08.060 --> 00:26:10.083
just as she was providing this counsel for

00:26:10.103 --> 00:26:10.462
her son?

00:26:13.119 --> 00:26:15.121
So in the judgment and desire,

00:26:15.161 --> 00:26:16.241
the mind and heart,

00:26:16.321 --> 00:26:17.982
even the thoughts and emotions of her

00:26:18.022 --> 00:26:22.365
husband, her ba'al, Lord and master,

00:26:24.306 --> 00:26:26.267
he never lacks for anything.

00:26:27.268 --> 00:26:28.929
He never ceases to prosper.

00:26:29.749 --> 00:26:31.190
He never stops benefiting.

00:26:31.931 --> 00:26:33.050
And he is never deprived,

00:26:33.852 --> 00:26:35.853
such that he is not without what he

00:26:35.913 --> 00:26:36.992
needs to prevail,

00:26:38.173 --> 00:26:40.095
particularly regarding the things deemed

00:26:40.194 --> 00:26:41.516
most valuable.

00:26:43.403 --> 00:26:44.723
That's Mashal, thirty-one eleven.

00:26:46.144 --> 00:26:48.164
This is brilliant counsel.

00:26:49.586 --> 00:26:55.147
Not only is it the great gift that

00:26:55.268 --> 00:26:57.468
a loving couple can bring to one another

00:26:58.249 --> 00:27:00.249
to be able to rely on each other

00:27:00.409 --> 00:27:02.630
and to help each other when we stumble

00:27:02.670 --> 00:27:03.109
and fall,

00:27:04.371 --> 00:27:09.412
because it is how we help one another

00:27:09.471 --> 00:27:11.932
develop the ability

00:27:13.153 --> 00:27:13.894
to get back up.

00:27:15.434 --> 00:27:20.076
It's how we instill a passion to succeed.

00:27:22.518 --> 00:27:24.678
It's how a burden is halved,

00:27:25.558 --> 00:27:26.578
a joy is doubled.

00:27:29.500 --> 00:27:31.040
And so she goes on to say that

00:27:33.001 --> 00:27:35.201
in the fullness of one's lab,

00:27:35.241 --> 00:27:37.722
which would be the mind and heart,

00:27:38.763 --> 00:27:40.183
the judgment and desire,

00:27:40.584 --> 00:27:41.744
the thoughts and emotions,

00:27:43.426 --> 00:27:44.126
of her husband,

00:27:44.968 --> 00:27:49.369
a woman who fills this role for her

00:27:49.410 --> 00:27:49.851
husband,

00:27:51.511 --> 00:27:53.393
assures that he never lacks for anything.

00:27:56.294 --> 00:27:57.654
He never ceases to prosper.

00:27:58.996 --> 00:28:02.857
If you are buttressed by a brilliant and

00:28:02.897 --> 00:28:03.538
reliable,

00:28:04.419 --> 00:28:08.480
trustworthy woman who has your best

00:28:08.560 --> 00:28:11.663
interests at heart, you will prosper.

00:28:13.257 --> 00:28:14.637
You will never stop benefiting.

00:28:14.718 --> 00:28:17.479
You'll never be deprived.

00:28:17.519 --> 00:28:20.800
You'll not ever go without what you need

00:28:20.941 --> 00:28:22.761
to prevail.

00:28:22.842 --> 00:28:25.324
And that is particularly true when dealing

00:28:25.344 --> 00:28:29.685
with the most valuable things in life.

00:28:29.705 --> 00:28:35.108
This remarkable Em said that a reliable

00:28:35.309 --> 00:28:41.093
wife whose mindset is to provide these

00:28:41.452 --> 00:28:42.854
marvelous gifts

00:28:44.451 --> 00:28:47.531
She acts in a way that yields to

00:28:47.772 --> 00:28:50.394
and serves him so as to treat him

00:28:50.433 --> 00:28:52.194
properly, beautifully, and productively.

00:28:52.974 --> 00:28:56.757
And he is never, she is,

00:28:56.856 --> 00:28:58.938
I should say, never harmful, troubling,

00:28:58.978 --> 00:28:59.557
disagreeable,

00:28:59.577 --> 00:29:01.179
or hindersome all the days of her life.

00:29:02.578 --> 00:29:05.361
For those that think that a woman being

00:29:05.421 --> 00:29:05.921
submissive

00:29:07.078 --> 00:29:11.801
to her husband in this way is somehow

00:29:12.022 --> 00:29:14.584
out of step with modern sensibilities.

00:29:15.924 --> 00:29:18.227
May I remind you of what Yahowah said

00:29:18.366 --> 00:29:19.907
just a moment ago,

00:29:19.968 --> 00:29:21.068
and excuse me one second.

00:29:23.471 --> 00:29:25.251
My dog was biting herself again.

00:29:27.798 --> 00:29:28.799
that Yahowah,

00:29:29.780 --> 00:29:33.343
in a Mizmowr that Dowd had written,

00:29:33.442 --> 00:29:34.644
it was actually Dowd who said,

00:29:35.304 --> 00:29:36.345
I want to thank you, Yahowah,

00:29:36.365 --> 00:29:37.405
for supporting me,

00:29:37.806 --> 00:29:39.586
for giving me everything that I needed.

00:29:40.488 --> 00:29:43.089
Yahowah puts himself in this same position

00:29:43.130 --> 00:29:44.009
relative to us.

00:29:44.631 --> 00:29:47.531
His goal is to offer us what we

00:29:47.571 --> 00:29:50.153
need to succeed.

00:29:50.193 --> 00:29:50.354
Now,

00:29:50.374 --> 00:29:51.775
I don't think you would ever say that

00:29:51.815 --> 00:29:54.116
Yahowah is subservient to man, would you?

00:29:55.068 --> 00:29:57.569
And yet that's the mindset that God has

00:29:57.589 --> 00:29:59.391
towards our relationship when we become

00:29:59.431 --> 00:30:00.251
part of his family.

00:30:00.892 --> 00:30:02.792
It's what parents do for their children.

00:30:03.093 --> 00:30:04.874
It's what spouses do for one another.

00:30:05.973 --> 00:30:07.894
And that is what is being conveyed here.

00:30:08.596 --> 00:30:10.676
That sometimes the best way to accomplish

00:30:10.696 --> 00:30:13.198
something worthwhile is to offer to

00:30:13.258 --> 00:30:16.259
support somebody who is engaged in doing

00:30:16.299 --> 00:30:17.220
something worthwhile.

00:30:18.621 --> 00:30:22.222
And that is what this Em is recommending

00:30:22.262 --> 00:30:22.823
for her son.

00:30:24.073 --> 00:30:25.753
Don't choose somebody who's conniving,

00:30:25.773 --> 00:30:28.336
who's trying to milk you for all you

00:30:28.375 --> 00:30:29.076
have to give.

