01:00:09.510 --> 01:00:12.153
over seven years.

01:00:12.173 --> 01:00:13.215
It's also her husband.

01:00:14.836 --> 01:00:15.838
They do this together.

01:00:16.398 --> 01:00:19.461
They are modeling for Dowd what he is

01:00:19.501 --> 01:00:20.742
to model for the rest of us.

01:00:21.603 --> 01:00:24.027
They're modeling for all who would be part

01:00:24.047 --> 01:00:24.686
of the covenant,

01:00:25.407 --> 01:00:26.989
precisely what God is looking for.

01:00:28.715 --> 01:00:30.255
And I've said this so many times and

01:00:30.275 --> 01:00:31.175
I'm going to repeat myself.

01:00:31.376 --> 01:00:33.356
I understand that there are those who

01:00:33.396 --> 01:00:34.996
think that if you're serving as an

01:00:35.056 --> 01:00:35.597
example,

01:00:35.916 --> 01:00:37.918
then your life needs to be near perfect.

01:00:38.057 --> 01:00:40.318
And that is not true.

01:00:40.498 --> 01:00:43.059
God does not want us to be perfect.

01:00:43.820 --> 01:00:44.599
If we were perfect,

01:00:44.639 --> 01:00:46.400
it would be horrendously

01:00:47.141 --> 01:00:49.501
counterproductive.

01:00:49.521 --> 01:00:51.983
The environment in Eden was perfect and it

01:00:52.023 --> 01:00:56.344
forestalled Adam's growth.

01:00:58.266 --> 01:01:01.467
You cannot succeed in a perfect

01:01:01.507 --> 01:01:03.387
environment.

01:01:03.467 --> 01:01:04.847
Not possible.

01:01:04.887 --> 01:01:07.489
Because to succeed, to grow,

01:01:07.588 --> 01:01:08.588
to be of value,

01:01:08.648 --> 01:01:10.148
to show that you can be trusted,

01:01:10.568 --> 01:01:12.769
to become worthy, to make a contribution,

01:01:13.130 --> 01:01:14.791
there must be things to overcome.

01:01:15.110 --> 01:01:17.411
There must be mistakes so that you can

01:01:17.471 --> 01:01:18.512
learn and grow.

01:01:19.251 --> 01:01:20.811
You must trip and fall so you can

01:01:20.871 --> 01:01:23.353
demonstrate the will and ability to get

01:01:23.393 --> 01:01:23.793
back up.

01:01:26.175 --> 01:01:27.856
These are things that are essential.

01:01:28.836 --> 01:01:30.518
It is only when we fail that we

01:01:30.559 --> 01:01:32.900
can prove that we have the moxie to

01:01:32.940 --> 01:01:35.784
be successful.

01:01:35.903 --> 01:01:38.385
It is our imperfections that make us

01:01:38.425 --> 01:01:42.769
interesting, that give us character.

01:01:45.278 --> 01:01:48.561
And so that is what we're here to

01:01:48.661 --> 01:01:49.001
model.

01:01:49.322 --> 01:01:52.463
We're here to show that Yahowah was

01:01:52.523 --> 01:01:55.465
explicit relative to the garden.

01:01:56.186 --> 01:02:00.588
He wanted four things from Adam and Adam

01:02:00.628 --> 01:02:01.989
delivered none of the four.

01:02:02.610 --> 01:02:05.811
And God caused the fall of man so

01:02:05.831 --> 01:02:09.393
that we could eventually figure out how to

01:02:09.594 --> 01:02:11.014
resolve the fall

01:02:11.195 --> 01:02:14.735
What Dowd ran, well, in this case Dowd,

01:02:14.775 --> 01:02:18.538
but what Adam failed to achieve.

01:02:20.298 --> 01:02:22.599
That's what Dowd at this moment is failing

01:02:22.619 --> 01:02:23.139
to achieve.

01:02:24.320 --> 01:02:26.181
That we can be observant.

01:02:26.340 --> 01:02:27.842
We can pay attention to what's happening

01:02:27.862 --> 01:02:30.802
around us.

01:02:30.902 --> 01:02:33.264
Listening to God,

01:02:33.324 --> 01:02:36.545
reading his testimony and applying it to

01:02:36.625 --> 01:02:37.824
everything that's happening around us so

01:02:37.844 --> 01:02:38.885
we're not oblivious

01:02:41.048 --> 01:02:41.188
Now,

01:02:41.228 --> 01:02:43.650
I spend as much time studying the world

01:02:43.690 --> 01:02:45.271
around us as I do studying the word

01:02:45.311 --> 01:02:45.692
of God,

01:02:45.731 --> 01:02:48.293
because the word of our God has to

01:02:48.333 --> 01:02:52.454
apply and be interjected into this real

01:02:52.494 --> 01:02:53.376
world of ours.

01:02:53.715 --> 01:02:56.336
You need to know the contrast between what

01:02:56.356 --> 01:02:58.077
he's offering and what man's offering.

01:02:58.679 --> 01:02:59.778
You need to be observant,

01:03:00.320 --> 01:03:01.219
first and foremost.

01:03:01.800 --> 01:03:03.862
And when God says, Shamar,

01:03:03.981 --> 01:03:05.702
I want you to be observant,

01:03:05.722 --> 01:03:08.563
and when he spoke of that specifically to

01:03:08.724 --> 01:03:09.704
Adam, the first man,

01:03:10.967 --> 01:03:13.327
with the neshamah created in the image of

01:03:13.407 --> 01:03:13.728
God.

01:03:14.869 --> 01:03:18.391
Shamar is equal parts closely examining

01:03:19.351 --> 01:03:20.532
and carefully considering.

01:03:21.952 --> 01:03:23.233
It's to see and think.

01:03:25.135 --> 01:03:28.777
So God wants us to perceive what's

01:03:28.818 --> 01:03:30.498
happening around us and to consider it.

01:03:32.480 --> 01:03:33.900
And then comes the important part.

01:03:35.380 --> 01:03:36.322
He wants us to respond.

01:03:38.679 --> 01:03:39.940
For there to be a relationship,

01:03:40.001 --> 01:03:42.362
we must engage.

01:03:42.461 --> 01:03:45.503
A one-sided relationship is an oxymoron.

01:03:46.403 --> 01:03:47.565
It's counterproductive.

01:03:48.224 --> 01:03:50.965
The person who is doing nothing is an

01:03:51.025 --> 01:03:56.108
entitled brat, a dependent, a negative,

01:03:56.268 --> 01:03:57.070
a parasite.

01:03:57.949 --> 01:03:59.130
God's not interested in that.

01:03:59.490 --> 01:04:02.492
He wants us to be making a contribution.

01:04:02.793 --> 01:04:04.353
He wants us to be engaged in the

01:04:04.393 --> 01:04:05.393
family business.

01:04:06.704 --> 01:04:09.105
He wants us to participate,

01:04:09.144 --> 01:04:10.005
to work with him,

01:04:10.324 --> 01:04:11.545
to make a better world,

01:04:11.585 --> 01:04:15.166
to make a better relationship.

01:04:15.186 --> 01:04:18.106
He wants us to be like the husband

01:04:18.126 --> 01:04:21.228
and wife that this Em is discussing before

01:04:21.748 --> 01:04:25.608
the very son of God.

01:04:25.708 --> 01:04:27.228
And then after those three things,

01:04:28.449 --> 01:04:29.670
to be observant, to be thoughtful,

01:04:30.110 --> 01:04:32.570
to be responsive,

01:04:32.590 --> 01:04:34.251
God needs us to be responsible.

01:04:36.239 --> 01:04:37.521
that when we make a mistake,

01:04:37.701 --> 01:04:39.001
that we're willing to correct it,

01:04:39.081 --> 01:04:40.342
we're willing to learn from it.

01:04:40.362 --> 01:04:41.643
When we stumble and fall,

01:04:41.684 --> 01:04:44.646
that we demonstrate the will to get up

01:04:45.186 --> 01:04:46.148
and get going again.

01:04:47.268 --> 01:04:48.429
Those are the four things.

01:04:49.610 --> 01:04:53.494
These are the things that the Ems Baal

01:04:54.414 --> 01:05:00.380
as Yada taught this woman, now his wife.

01:05:01.291 --> 01:05:05.373
and perhaps also impressed upon his

01:05:05.414 --> 01:05:07.215
adoptive son, Dowd.

01:05:09.016 --> 01:05:09.215
Dowd,

01:05:09.235 --> 01:05:10.856
the man who did not know his mother

01:05:10.876 --> 01:05:13.838
and was rejected by his father,

01:05:15.239 --> 01:05:18.320
was appointed a mother and father that

01:05:18.400 --> 01:05:22.083
modeled the very behaviors that God was

01:05:22.163 --> 01:05:25.045
looking for from his son.

01:05:28.237 --> 01:05:30.097
This goes on to say in the twenty-fourth

01:05:30.137 --> 01:05:31.878
statement of the thirty-first and final

01:05:31.918 --> 01:05:32.398
Mashal,

01:05:33.259 --> 01:05:36.119
linen garments which envelop wrap and

01:05:36.179 --> 01:05:36.539
cover.

01:05:37.260 --> 01:05:39.521
She is made, she values,

01:05:39.961 --> 01:05:41.722
and she is offering as a quid pro

01:05:41.782 --> 01:05:42.103
quo,

01:05:43.342 --> 01:05:45.903
surrendering and transferring possession

01:05:45.963 --> 01:05:48.304
of these highly treasured garments.

01:05:48.965 --> 01:05:51.945
The celebratory slashes in preparation for

01:05:51.967 --> 01:05:53.786
the chag feast, the chagowr,

01:05:54.327 --> 01:05:55.407
she offers as a gift.

01:05:57.458 --> 01:05:58.440
To the Canaanite,

01:05:59.360 --> 01:06:02.802
this merchant salesman of hers,

01:06:02.842 --> 01:06:03.362
her husband.

01:06:06.704 --> 01:06:12.228
Yes, God wants his family leaders,

01:06:13.548 --> 01:06:14.969
his exemplars.

01:06:15.990 --> 01:06:17.351
He wants them dressed in linen.

01:06:18.672 --> 01:06:20.634
They will be wearing lay-aware clothes.

01:06:22.260 --> 01:06:25.922
They will be positioned to celebrate the

01:06:25.961 --> 01:06:30.224
chag, the chag Matsah and chag Sukah,

01:06:30.403 --> 01:06:32.425
the spring and fall feasts,

01:06:34.664 --> 01:06:35.985
dressed for success,

01:06:37.146 --> 01:06:39.547
dressed in the very garment of luminosity

01:06:39.567 --> 01:06:44.028
that I spoke of, um, twenty years ago.

01:06:46.228 --> 01:06:46.969
They're her gift.

01:06:48.469 --> 01:06:50.451
And they are offered by way of the

01:06:52.023 --> 01:06:54.643
merchant salesman of her husband that he

01:06:54.704 --> 01:06:59.347
now can dole out to every covenant member

01:06:59.367 --> 01:07:00.626
and he's not going to give them away

01:07:00.666 --> 01:07:00.987
free.

01:07:01.748 --> 01:07:04.309
Nope.

01:07:04.349 --> 01:07:08.130
He's not going to charge money for them,

01:07:08.170 --> 01:07:10.811
but he'll elicit a price because he knows

01:07:10.851 --> 01:07:13.773
that if we don't invest in something,

01:07:13.793 --> 01:07:15.114
if we don't contribute to it,

01:07:15.175 --> 01:07:15.974
we don't value it.

01:07:17.286 --> 01:07:18.728
So I can assure you this,

01:07:19.449 --> 01:07:21.690
that she is offering them through her,

01:07:22.612 --> 01:07:23.112
Cain and I,

01:07:23.172 --> 01:07:26.956
merchant salesman of a husband for these

01:07:26.996 --> 01:07:27.777
child feasts,

01:07:28.737 --> 01:07:31.059
because he knows that they can't be given

01:07:31.099 --> 01:07:33.141
away,

01:07:33.181 --> 01:07:35.543
that they must be earned to be

01:07:35.583 --> 01:07:38.686
appreciated.

01:07:38.746 --> 01:07:39.266
And so you say,

01:07:39.507 --> 01:07:40.568
what is he gonna charge for them?

01:07:40.648 --> 01:07:41.768
I just told you, it's not money.

01:07:41.789 --> 01:07:43.610
He won't have any use for that.

01:07:44.958 --> 01:07:46.840
And he's never charged for his books.

01:07:46.860 --> 01:07:48.721
You can go to yadayah.com.

01:07:48.740 --> 01:07:51.043
Every single book in its entirety is free.

01:07:51.182 --> 01:07:52.043
Yadayah.com.

01:07:52.083 --> 01:07:52.423
Go there.

01:07:52.965 --> 01:07:53.385
Check it out.

01:07:53.945 --> 01:07:56.306
Every book is free.

01:07:56.327 --> 01:07:58.108
There's not even a donate button on the

01:07:58.148 --> 01:07:58.449
site.

01:07:59.048 --> 01:07:59.469
How's that?

01:08:02.411 --> 01:08:04.994
But I also know that those who do

01:08:05.034 --> 01:08:08.016
not contribute for what they are given

01:08:08.157 --> 01:08:09.016
don't appreciate it.

01:08:10.659 --> 01:08:13.380
And so I will elicit a contribution.

01:08:15.646 --> 01:08:16.987
And it will be very similar to the

01:08:17.027 --> 01:08:19.488
contribution that Yahowah has sought.

01:08:19.569 --> 01:08:21.329
Cause I have found that if you go

01:08:21.369 --> 01:08:23.190
to where his words lead,

01:08:23.251 --> 01:08:26.432
if you embody what he is offering and

01:08:26.493 --> 01:08:30.055
expects in return, you can't be wrong.

01:08:30.095 --> 01:08:31.296
So I know the fair price.

01:08:32.817 --> 01:08:33.978
You want one of these garments?

01:08:34.978 --> 01:08:38.159
Be observant, be thoughtful,

01:08:38.199 --> 01:08:40.761
be responsive and be responsible.

01:08:44.814 --> 01:08:47.355
Oz, of course, by Ba'oz.

01:08:48.716 --> 01:08:50.797
Strength and fortitude, dignity,

01:08:51.398 --> 01:08:52.779
and a most beautiful appearance,

01:08:52.798 --> 01:08:54.840
a noble status and character.

01:08:54.859 --> 01:08:56.381
Ah, they adorn her.

01:08:57.341 --> 01:09:00.023
She will be the most beautiful of all

01:09:00.082 --> 01:09:00.543
of the women.

01:09:02.564 --> 01:09:05.207
And so she is amused and entertained,

01:09:05.266 --> 01:09:07.207
smiling and laughing during the day to

01:09:07.247 --> 01:09:07.507
come,

01:09:07.568 --> 01:09:09.529
at long last and throughout the future.

01:09:10.229 --> 01:09:11.270
She is the exemplar.

01:09:12.911 --> 01:09:13.872
She's the most beautiful.

01:09:15.327 --> 01:09:17.307
Woman, inside and out,

01:09:17.427 --> 01:09:19.349
the most noble of character,

01:09:19.569 --> 01:09:20.949
the most beautiful of appearance,

01:09:21.670 --> 01:09:22.850
the most dignified.

01:09:24.412 --> 01:09:26.233
It amuses her, entertains her.

01:09:26.472 --> 01:09:28.194
She's going to smile and laugh because she

01:09:28.234 --> 01:09:31.354
knows that there is a benefit for all

01:09:32.055 --> 01:09:34.436
when she models these things.

01:09:38.359 --> 01:09:41.159
She opens her mouth with wisdom.

01:09:41.880 --> 01:09:42.421
Chokmah.

01:09:43.416 --> 01:09:45.676
intelligently revealing the capacity to

01:09:45.756 --> 01:09:46.617
understand.

01:09:47.697 --> 01:09:50.377
You see, it's brains and beauty.

01:09:51.578 --> 01:09:53.259
She's as bright as she is beautiful.

01:09:54.619 --> 01:09:55.579
She has chokmah.

01:09:58.841 --> 01:10:00.501
And a loyal love and affection,

01:10:01.181 --> 01:10:03.181
showing great favoritism and devotion,

01:10:03.221 --> 01:10:05.863
Chesed, for the Towrah,

01:10:06.823 --> 01:10:07.884
the guidance and teaching,

01:10:07.904 --> 01:10:09.984
the instructions and directions of Yahowah.

01:10:10.645 --> 01:10:12.045
They are what's on her tongue.

01:10:15.505 --> 01:10:17.827
Leah, given the option, wouldn't sleep.

01:10:18.988 --> 01:10:21.470
She would do Towrah twenty-four-seven.

01:10:22.850 --> 01:10:24.773
She devours it.

01:10:24.813 --> 01:10:25.753
She loves it.

01:10:25.854 --> 01:10:29.036
She lives in its pages.

01:10:30.337 --> 01:10:32.679
And she recognizes something that we've

01:10:32.719 --> 01:10:34.860
all come to embrace.

01:10:34.900 --> 01:10:35.902
The prophets are Towrah.

01:10:37.002 --> 01:10:38.024
The Mizmowr are Towrah.

01:10:38.942 --> 01:10:41.042
Every inspired word of our God,

01:10:41.444 --> 01:10:43.125
as he has communicated through men and

01:10:43.145 --> 01:10:44.125
women of his choice,

01:10:44.845 --> 01:10:49.908
contain his Towrah teaching and guidance.

01:10:49.948 --> 01:10:51.128
So now as she seeks,

01:10:51.510 --> 01:10:53.850
how am I to fulfill this role to

01:10:53.930 --> 01:10:57.752
the utmost of our collective

01:10:57.773 --> 01:10:58.654
collaboration?

01:11:00.515 --> 01:11:02.195
She turns to the Towrah for guidance and

01:11:02.216 --> 01:11:02.576
teaching.

01:11:03.697 --> 01:11:04.917
Just as I want to know how to

01:11:04.957 --> 01:11:07.719
do this job, I turn to my pal,

01:11:07.798 --> 01:11:08.319
Yasha'yah.

01:11:09.140 --> 01:11:10.721
He's written the textbook on the subject.

01:11:12.122 --> 01:11:14.503
And now we hear that this is the

01:11:14.583 --> 01:11:20.947
most complete of all women.

01:11:20.987 --> 01:11:23.427
She's wise, she's beautiful,

01:11:24.188 --> 01:11:24.889
and she's loving.

01:11:27.029 --> 01:11:34.493
Wise, beautiful, and loving.

01:11:34.512 --> 01:11:35.394
And as a result,

01:11:36.592 --> 01:11:40.136
or perhaps as the cause, perhaps both.

01:11:40.997 --> 01:11:43.300
The Towrah is always on her tongue.

01:11:44.480 --> 01:11:46.002
Sweet is honey.

01:11:49.025 --> 01:11:51.948
She keeps watch, always on the lookout,

01:11:52.630 --> 01:11:55.412
and hopeful expectation for improved

01:11:55.472 --> 01:11:55.993
results.

01:11:57.229 --> 01:11:58.712
And the ways,

01:11:58.771 --> 01:12:00.774
the walk and the affairs of her family

01:12:00.795 --> 01:12:01.215
and home.

01:12:01.895 --> 01:12:04.840
She does not consume or feed upon the

01:12:04.939 --> 01:12:07.543
bread of conflict of those who lack

01:12:07.583 --> 01:12:09.725
discipline or who are immoral,

01:12:09.966 --> 01:12:11.307
the idle or the lazy.

01:12:12.181 --> 01:12:13.542
without the initiative to make a

01:12:13.622 --> 01:12:14.462
contribution.

01:12:14.563 --> 01:12:18.403
Boy, isn't this true?

01:12:18.462 --> 01:12:19.944
Maya's always on the lookout.

01:12:20.703 --> 01:12:23.243
She's hopeful that she will continue to

01:12:23.305 --> 01:12:26.524
encounter those who exceed expectations,

01:12:26.564 --> 01:12:28.426
who are willing to engage,

01:12:28.466 --> 01:12:31.565
who bring aptitude and attitude to the

01:12:31.605 --> 01:12:32.046
family,

01:12:32.086 --> 01:12:36.747
who are self-motivated and know that when

01:12:36.807 --> 01:12:38.228
we make a contribution,

01:12:38.948 --> 01:12:40.389
on behalf of Yahowah,

01:12:40.529 --> 01:12:42.530
his son and the Towrah,

01:12:42.690 --> 01:12:45.573
the covenant family that is appreciated by

01:12:45.632 --> 01:12:48.755
our God and that these contributions never

01:12:48.815 --> 01:12:52.578
go unrewarded.

01:12:52.757 --> 01:12:55.701
And so she is completely devoted to the

01:12:55.740 --> 01:12:57.301
affairs of her family,

01:12:57.341 --> 01:12:58.483
that's the covenant family.

01:13:00.277 --> 01:13:00.877
And as a result,

01:13:01.717 --> 01:13:03.537
she doesn't feed upon the bread of

01:13:03.597 --> 01:13:04.118
conflict.

01:13:04.917 --> 01:13:06.998
And she doesn't spend any time with those

01:13:07.019 --> 01:13:09.139
who lack discipline, who are immoral.

01:13:09.920 --> 01:13:11.220
If you're lazy and idle,

01:13:11.920 --> 01:13:13.940
you're not gonna find Leah responsive.

01:13:14.541 --> 01:13:15.940
You need to take the initiative,

01:13:16.161 --> 01:13:19.622
make a contribution.

01:13:19.641 --> 01:13:21.301
Her children will rise up,

01:13:21.582 --> 01:13:22.622
they will take a stand.

01:13:23.743 --> 01:13:25.082
And as a result of all of this,

01:13:25.122 --> 01:13:27.524
they're going to call her Ashar.

01:13:29.069 --> 01:13:30.751
going to call her a beneficial blessing

01:13:31.591 --> 01:13:35.435
for having revealed the way to capitalize

01:13:35.475 --> 01:13:37.657
on this relationship.

01:13:37.676 --> 01:13:39.158
They will call her Ashar,

01:13:40.559 --> 01:13:41.840
and they're going to call her husband,

01:13:42.100 --> 01:13:45.103
Ba'al, a lord and master too.

01:13:46.743 --> 01:13:49.246
He reflects her bright and clear light and

01:13:49.306 --> 01:13:51.528
consistently praises her extolling her

01:13:51.587 --> 01:13:52.029
virtues.

01:13:53.512 --> 01:13:56.234
Now we've made very clear that Yahowah does

01:13:56.293 --> 01:13:58.033
not want to be called a Lord because

01:13:58.073 --> 01:13:59.914
he prefers being known as our father.

01:14:01.354 --> 01:14:04.076
And it is a fatherly role that I'm

01:14:04.115 --> 01:14:06.617
being asked to play beside the Amah

01:14:06.676 --> 01:14:08.497
mother, this Ashar,

01:14:09.096 --> 01:14:11.478
for the covenant family and for those who

01:14:11.537 --> 01:14:15.019
are being invited to return to Eden and

01:14:15.059 --> 01:14:18.579
to model the four responses that Yahowah

01:14:18.600 --> 01:14:19.220
was looking for.

01:14:20.894 --> 01:14:22.555
And in that regard,

01:14:22.614 --> 01:14:23.774
there is an honorarium.

01:14:23.935 --> 01:14:28.377
And this title is one that was used

01:14:28.396 --> 01:14:31.018
throughout time to say essentially, yes,

01:14:31.038 --> 01:14:31.298
sir.

01:14:33.059 --> 01:14:34.260
Back in my day,

01:14:34.319 --> 01:14:38.002
when you were speaking to someone who was

01:14:38.122 --> 01:14:40.162
older and who had achieved something in

01:14:40.662 --> 01:14:42.724
their life that was sharing insights with

01:14:42.743 --> 01:14:47.286
you and being generous with you,

01:14:47.345 --> 01:14:49.667
you would show them the respect of saying,

01:14:49.686 --> 01:14:49.966
yes, sir.

01:14:50.930 --> 01:14:52.990
And that's sort of what this means.

01:14:53.030 --> 01:14:56.453
But it also means that God knows that

01:14:57.493 --> 01:15:00.854
we humans, even in a perfect environment,

01:15:00.875 --> 01:15:02.114
which the Garden of Eden is going to

01:15:02.154 --> 01:15:04.195
provide when the whole earth is

01:15:04.235 --> 01:15:05.636
transformed to those conditions,

01:15:06.117 --> 01:15:07.797
we still need leadership.

01:15:09.037 --> 01:15:10.298
Dowd's going to be our king.

01:15:10.899 --> 01:15:13.560
He's going to be the sovereign of

01:15:13.600 --> 01:15:14.220
forevermore.

01:15:15.301 --> 01:15:18.462
But even Dowd needs leadership.

01:15:19.954 --> 01:15:21.416
Uh, and, um,

01:15:21.655 --> 01:15:24.997
so do all of those who will be

01:15:25.057 --> 01:15:26.519
part of this covenant family.

01:15:26.578 --> 01:15:29.640
And so this is to say that, oh,

01:15:29.680 --> 01:15:34.264
this person is going to be such that

01:15:34.684 --> 01:15:38.166
just as Leah is perceived as the

01:15:38.206 --> 01:15:42.247
beneficial one who offers the blessings of

01:15:42.307 --> 01:15:43.708
the covenant,

01:15:44.729 --> 01:15:46.730
that her husband's going to be known as

01:15:46.770 --> 01:15:48.511
bail, the Lord and master.

01:15:50.480 --> 01:15:51.922
Many women have acted,

01:15:52.463 --> 01:15:57.128
engaged and performed aptly and ably,

01:15:57.970 --> 01:15:59.752
demonstrating the power of their

01:15:59.792 --> 01:16:00.453
convictions.

01:16:01.494 --> 01:16:03.197
This is a powerful thing for Dowd to

01:16:03.216 --> 01:16:05.579
say because he had never experienced a

01:16:05.640 --> 01:16:05.880
woman

01:16:06.701 --> 01:16:08.662
who performed ably or aptly,

01:16:09.483 --> 01:16:11.724
never had a relationship with a woman who

01:16:11.743 --> 01:16:14.046
had the power of her convictions,

01:16:14.206 --> 01:16:15.646
never met a noble woman,

01:16:16.167 --> 01:16:17.887
capable and competent.

01:16:17.967 --> 01:16:18.509
If he had,

01:16:18.569 --> 01:16:21.109
he disregarded them and he never looked

01:16:21.189 --> 01:16:24.672
more than skin deep.

01:16:24.693 --> 01:16:27.154
But this woman got his attention.

01:16:28.114 --> 01:16:30.155
This woman was far more than just

01:16:30.176 --> 01:16:31.136
physically beautiful.

01:16:31.979 --> 01:16:34.542
She was brilliant and she had character

01:16:35.341 --> 01:16:38.283
and she had conviction and she was

01:16:38.323 --> 01:16:38.864
competent.

01:16:39.784 --> 01:16:42.447
And so he said of her in an

01:16:42.487 --> 01:16:44.087
inspired text from Yahowah,

01:16:45.248 --> 01:16:47.890
you yourself surpass and rise,

01:16:48.971 --> 01:16:53.534
ascending above and are exalted above them

01:16:53.595 --> 01:16:56.237
all.

01:16:56.277 --> 01:16:57.797
Mashal, thirty-one, twenty-nine.

01:17:02.051 --> 01:17:02.532
Therefore,

01:17:02.771 --> 01:17:08.274
the disingenuous in the vein of compassion

01:17:08.335 --> 01:17:12.136
and favoritism that seek popular appeal,

01:17:13.657 --> 01:17:15.518
they are meaningless, they are futile.

01:17:17.137 --> 01:17:19.439
Because it's all about a woman who is

01:17:19.498 --> 01:17:20.579
brilliant and beautiful,

01:17:21.699 --> 01:17:24.320
who reveres and respects Yahowah.

01:17:25.902 --> 01:17:29.002
It is she who is to be independently

01:17:29.042 --> 01:17:30.684
admired and celebrated.

01:17:31.583 --> 01:17:32.484
without compulsion,

01:17:33.545 --> 01:17:36.667
all for radiating her beautiful,

01:17:36.867 --> 01:17:39.429
brilliant, and clear light.

01:17:42.591 --> 01:17:44.952
And as the fruit of her hands,

01:17:45.652 --> 01:17:47.993
those of you who are harvested into the

01:17:48.033 --> 01:17:48.814
covenant family,

01:17:49.935 --> 01:17:54.297
you all have decided to be entrusted to

01:17:54.337 --> 01:17:55.177
her as a gift.

01:17:56.378 --> 01:17:58.460
And you should now choose to be productive

01:17:58.479 --> 01:17:58.939
for her.

01:18:00.942 --> 01:18:01.242
And so,

01:18:02.421 --> 01:18:05.381
Her contributions and accomplishments will

01:18:05.421 --> 01:18:08.783
exclaim that she is praiseworthy by

01:18:08.823 --> 01:18:11.083
acknowledging her brilliant radiance and

01:18:11.123 --> 01:18:11.724
clear light.

01:18:12.764 --> 01:18:13.104
Also,

01:18:15.005 --> 01:18:17.945
within that inter-sanctum of the

01:18:18.046 --> 01:18:22.207
thoughtful assembly of those who think

01:18:22.587 --> 01:18:23.188
rationally.

01:18:26.488 --> 01:18:30.189
The conclusion of the final word picture.

01:18:32.078 --> 01:18:35.962
Now I am thankful that Yahowah waited to

01:18:37.122 --> 01:18:40.444
the very end to present his gift,

01:18:41.506 --> 01:18:45.048
enabling us to unwrap her with loving

01:18:45.069 --> 01:18:49.051
care.

01:18:49.212 --> 01:18:53.636
It is true love,

01:18:55.256 --> 01:18:56.177
the love of a son,

01:18:57.819 --> 01:18:59.000
the support of a husband,

01:19:00.541 --> 01:19:01.481
the appreciation

01:19:02.730 --> 01:19:07.836
of our God and the contributions that we

01:19:07.876 --> 01:19:13.961
can make to his family.

01:19:14.001 --> 01:19:16.844
That is what we are commemorating with the

01:19:16.863 --> 01:19:20.386
final word picture.

01:19:20.466 --> 01:19:21.368
I thank you for listening.